==工业==

洛根市拥有大量的工业和商业区域，主要位于伍德里奇北部和东部，斯普林伍德和黛西山西部，聚集在洛根路，太平洋高速路和金士顿路之间的三角区域，并且沿着汉普顿路向西延伸。克瑞斯麦德工业区被设计用于轻型和中型的制造业部门。<ref>{{cite web|title=Crestmead industrial estate |url=http://www.dsdip.qld.gov.au/land-for-industry/crestmead-industrial-estate.html |publisher=[[Queensland_Government|Queensland Government]] |accessdate=24 May 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527233356/http://www.dsdip.qld.gov.au/land-for-industry/crestmead-industrial-estate.html |archivedate=27 May 2014 |df= }}</ref>

洛根是昆士兰的[[角子机|角子机]]之都，在41个注册地点拥有超过2128台机器。<ref>(28 August 2012) Tony Moore. [http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/queensland/logan-queenslands-pokies-capital-20120827-24wrn.html Logan Queensland's pokies capital] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920214159/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/queensland/logan-queenslands-pokies-capital-20120827-24wrn.html |date=20 September 2013 }}. Brisbane Times. Fairfax Media.</ref>

澳洲持续运作的最古老的[[朗姆酒|朗姆酒]]厂位于洛根的宾利地区。伴随着不断增加的的文化和体育活动，旅游业正在成为当地经济的重要贡献部门。

